Class Building

  • java.lang.Object
    • elevator.Building

  • public class Building
extends java.lang.Object
    Takes user inputs to create a Building with given number of customers and floors. Main simulates the running of the elevator for the Building created and it's customers.
    Version:
    SP2 CWK 3 2014
    Author:
    Nazia Ayeni and Aymar Bell Jr.
